%bridge-context: Lebensohl over 2-level overcalls of 1NT (fast denies); applies over 2C as well (no 'systems on')
{With 12 points opposite partner's 15-17, this is a forcing-to-game hand, so you bid 3\H. Don't think of it as a jump, just a 3-level bid showing at least 10 points and a 5+ card suit.  

Partner has 3-card support and is happy to bid game in that suit.}

